-- Bharti Airtel Offers to Acquire the Rest of Zain's Shares in Celtel Zambia
-- Young-Sam Cho
-- 2010-07-23T04:53:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-23/bharti-airtel-offers-to-acquire-the-rest-of-zain-s-shares-in-celtel-zambia.html

          
          
             (Corrects date to say July 20 in first paragraph.)  
 Bharti Airtel Ltd. offered to buy
Celtel Zambia Ltd. shares held by minority shareholders as part
of a mandatory offer, according to a regulatory filing dated
July 20.  
 The purchase will be made by Celtel Zambia Holdings B.V., a
wholly owned unit of Bharti Airtel, according to the statement.  
          
          


  


        